Good day,

My name is Sir Leonard Valentinovich Blavatnik. You are among the individua=
ls selected to receive a donation from my company, Access Industries.

I have decided to give $600,000.00 (Six Hundred Thousand United States Doll=
ars) each to randomly selected individuals worldwide. Upon receiving this e=
mail, you can consider yourself one of the lucky recipients. Your email add=
ress was selected randomly online.

Kindly reply at your earliest convenience so that I can confirm your email =
address is valid.

You can read more about me via the link below:
https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Len_Blavatnik

Warm Regards,
Sir Leonard Valentinovich Blavatnik
President, Access Industries



